rows.label: qst004002_msg0001
rows.name: I saw it! At Zeno's Deadbole!

rows.label: qst004002_msg0002
rows.name:
There's usually nothing
there, but it was shining!

rows.label: qst004002_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm sure they're hiding a
huge blade to break the
crane! Oh, how scary...

rows.label: qst004002_msg0004
rows.name:
And it's at times like these that
the Superbian soldiers do nothing!

rows.label: qst004002_msg0101
rows.name:
Superbia says they're
protecting Gula, but we've
never been protected, have we!

rows.label: qst004002_msg0102
rows.name:
My husband also swore when we
got married that he'd tell me
he loved me every day...

rows.label: qst004002_msg0103
rows.name:
He stopped after three days!
Honestly, what a useless husband!
